"{\"uid\": \"thesouthafrican.com-sport-paris-olympics-2024-size-of-zimbabwes-paris-olympic-2024-delegation-sparks-controversy\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Copyright Blue Sky Publications (Pty) Ltd. All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 63, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15, \"end\": 18, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.9921829174699442, \"rank\": 0.00786492209772031, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"thesouthafrican.com is a division of Blue Sky Publications Ltd. Reproduction without permission prohibited  Home\\u00bbSport\\u00bbParis Olympics 2024\\u00bbSize of Zimbabwe's Paris Olympic 2024 delegation sparks controversy  Zimbabwe have sought to dampen a furore sparked by reports that scores of officials accompanied a its seven-athlete Olympics team to Paris.\", \"from\": 65, \"to\": 412, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 107, \"end\": 110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.9921829174699442, \"rank\": 0.00786492209772031, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}, {\"begin\": 212, \"end\": 220, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zimbabwe\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7178212929888266e-40, \"text\": \"Zimbabwe\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zimbabwe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zimbabwe\"}, {\"begin\": 223, \"end\": 228, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999984661372, \"rank\": 1.5340896767127262e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 273, \"end\": 281, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zimbabwe\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7178212929888266e-40, \"text\": \"Zimbabwe\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zimbabwe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zimbabwe\"}, {\"begin\": 406, \"end\": 411, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999984661372, \"rank\": 1.5340896767127262e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Zimbabweon Thursday sought to dampen a furore sparked by reports that scores of officials accompanied a meagreseven-athleteOlympics team to Paris, saying most were not part of the official delegation.\", \"from\": 414, \"to\": 614, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 554, \"end\": 559, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999984661372, \"rank\": 1.5340896767127262e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the latest Paris Olympics 2024 news, bookmarkThe South African website'sdedicated section  The Zimbabwe Olympic Committee (ZOC) said onlyninestaff, including coaches and officials, travelled to France with the squad ahead of the opening ceremony on Friday, after many had vented their anger online at the alleged waste of public money.\", \"from\": 616, \"to\": 955, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 715, \"end\": 741, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zimbabwe_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Zimbabwe Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zimbabwe_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zimbabwe_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 743, \"end\": 746, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ZOC_(band)\", \"score\": 0.562270290011204, \"rank\": 0.5624999999999292, \"text\": \"ZOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ZOC_(band)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ZOC_(band)\"}, {\"begin\": 814, \"end\": 820, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.8226556652279934, \"rank\": 0.21231644521733628, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are aware though that there are many other technical officials, dignitaries invited to the games directly to officiate and as guests and many other hundreds of Zimbabweans in Paris in various capacities,\\\" said ZOC president Thabani Gonye.\", \"from\": 957, \"to\": 1199, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1136, \"end\": 1141, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999984661372, \"rank\": 1.5340896767127262e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1171, \"end\": 1174, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ZOC_(band)\", \"score\": 0.562270290011204, \"rank\": 0.5624999999999292, \"text\": \"ZOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ZOC_(band)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ZOC_(band)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"These are not part of Team Zimbabwe delegation but Zimbabweans all welcome and free to cheer our athletes on.\\\"\", \"from\": 1201, \"to\": 1312, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1229, \"end\": 1237, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zimbabwe\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7178212929888266e-40, \"text\": \"Zimbabwe\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zimbabwe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zimbabwe\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The statement came afterreportsthat the impoverished nation had sent, in some cases via private jet, a bloated delegation of more than 60 people, including Vice PresidentConstantino Chiwengaand Sports MinisterKirsty Coventry.\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1539, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1530, \"end\": 1538, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coventry\", \"score\": 0.9999836718926148, \"rank\": 1.6315749853874308e-05, \"text\": \"Coventry\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coventry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coventry\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The sheer size of the official delegation, particularly in contrast to the small number of athletes, raises serious questions about the government's priorities and resource allocation, especially at a time when it is begging for drought relief assistance from countries that sent huge teams of athletes with very few officials,\\\" prominent journalist and activist Hopewell Chin'onowrote on X.\", \"from\": 1541, \"to\": 1933, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1905, \"end\": 1913, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hopewell_tradition\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5488012449936665e-22, \"text\": \"Hopewell\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hopewell_tradition\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hopewell_tradition\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Former education minister Jonathan Moyo described it as an \\\"embarrassing dent on Zimbabwe's reputation\\\", while opposition politician Fadzayi Mahere argued taxpayers' money could have been better spent.\", \"from\": 1935, \"to\": 2136, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1961, \"end\": 1974, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Moyo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jonathan Moyo\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Moyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Moyo\"}, {\"begin\": 2016, \"end\": 2024, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zimbabwe\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7178212929888266e-40, \"text\": \"Zimbabwe\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zimbabwe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zimbabwe\"}, {\"begin\": 2068, \"end\": 2082, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fadzayi_Mahere\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Fadzayi Mahere\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fadzayi_Mahere\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fadzayi_Mahere\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Government spokesman Nick Mangwana said Vice President Chiwenga was in Paris for the Olympics' official opening and \\\"other business\\\" including luring investments, and Coventry was there as a member of the International Olympic Committee.\", \"from\": 2138, \"to\": 2375, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2159, \"end\": 2163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nick_Jonas\", \"score\": 0.9999991107565026, \"rank\": 8.87838748371883e-07, \"text\": \"Nick\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nick_Jonas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nick_Jonas\"}, {\"begin\": 2209, \"end\": 2214, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999984661372, \"rank\": 1.5340896767127262e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2305, \"end\": 2313, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coventry\", \"score\": 0.9999836718926148, \"rank\": 1.6315749853874308e-05, \"text\": \"Coventry\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coventry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coventry\"}, {\"begin\": 2343, \"end\": 2374, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International O